NAME
    OpusVL::AppKitX::PasswordReset - Provides a password reset URL, with
    defaults

DESCRIPTION
    Either:

    Add "+OpusVL::AppKitX::PasswordReset" to your Builder to use the
    defaults
    Extend "OpusVL::AppKitX::PasswordReset::Controller::PasswordReset" to
    alter the defaults.

    The aforementioned controller extends from
    CatalystX::SimpleLogin::Controller::Login, so you can replace your login
    controller with one of these.

